"Nothing=20in=20life=20is=20to=20be= =20feared;=20it=20is=20only=20to=20be=20understood.=20Now=20is=20the=20time=20t= o=20understand=20more=20so=20that=20we=20may=20fear=20less." =20Marie=20Curie

=

A=20quick=20reminder=20to=20read=20IRS=20Busin= ess=20Travel=20Expenses=20Topic=20511.=20The=20following=20is=20a=20quote:

 

<= p=20class=3D"cs95E872D0">“Travel=20expenses= =20are=20the=20ordinary=20and=20necessary=20expenses=20of=20traveling=20away=20= from=20home=20for=20your=20business,=20profession,=20or=20job.=20Generally,=20e= mployees=20deduct=20these=20expenses=20by=20using=20Form=202106=20(PDF),=20Employee=20Busi= ness=20Expenses,=20or=20Form=202106-EZ=20(PDF)<= /a>,=20= Unreimbursed=20Employee=20Business=20Expenses,=20and=20Form=201040,=20Schedule=20A=20(PDF),=20Itemized=20Deductions.=20You=20can't=20deduct=20expenses=20tha= t=20are=20lavish=20or=20extravagant,=20or=20that=20are=20for=20personal=20purpo= ses.”

&n= bsp;

Please=20= make=20sure=20that=20all=20staff=20is=20aware=20of=20our=20company=20policy=20r= egarding=20per-diems=20and=20travel=20reimbursements.

 

Sandy=20Bright

Benefits=20Coordinator

DevAV=20

Please=20don’t=20forget=20that=20we= =20need=20to=20schedule=20on-site=20training=20events=20with=20all=20major=20re= tailers.=20Our=20new=20products=20are=20not=20plug=20&=20play.=20We=20need= =20to=20teach=20salespeople=20how=20to=20hook=20up=20our=20television=20sets=20= and=20how=20to=20help=20customers=20with=20HDCP=20issues.=20

 

I=20hate=20HDCP=20–=20how=20about= =20you?

 =

High-bandwidt= h=20Digital=20Content=20Protection=20(HDCP)=20is=20a=20system=20designed=20to= =20protect=20digital=20content.=20The=20technology=20is=20intended=20to=20prote= ct=20unauthorized=20duplication=20of=20high=20definition=20(HD)=20video=20and= =20audio=20as=20it=20travels=20across=20connections—from=20your=20compute= r=20to=20your=20TV=20or=20monitor,=20for=20example.=20Your=20setup,=20from=20de= vices=20to=20displays=20to=20cables,=20adapters,=20and=20software=20drivers,=20= must=20all=20be=20HDCP=20compliant=20in=20order=20to=20watch=20HD-quality=20vid= eos=20with=20HBO=20GO.   =20= Source:=20HBO.com

 

See=20you=20soon…

“A=20valve=20amplifier=20or=20tube=20amplifier=20is=20a=20type=20of=20electronic=20amplifier=20that=20uses=20vacuum=20tubes=20to=20increase=20the=20amplitude=20or=20power=20of=20a= =20signal.=20Low=20to= =20medium=20power=20valve=20amplifiers=20for=20frequencies=20below=20the=20microwaves=20were=20largely=20replaced=20by=20solid=20st= ate=20amplifiers=20during=20the= =201960s=20and=201970s.=20Valve=20amplifiers=20are=20used=20for=20applications= =20such=20as=20guitar=20amplifiers,=20satellite=20trans= ponders=20such=20as=20DirecTV=20and=20GPS,=20audiophile=20stereo=20amplifiers,=20military=20a= pplications=20(such=20as=20radar)=20and=20very=20high=20power=20radio=20and=20UHF=20= television=20transmitters.”

Looks=20like=20I’m=20not=20going=20to=20make=20my=20deadline.=20= Will=20you=20be=20able=20to=20help=20me=20finish=20the=20specifications=20for= =20our=20new=20power=20supply?=20As=20you=20know,=20work=20on=20our=20next=20ge= neration=20amplifier=20cannot=20proceed=20without=20a=20more=20efficient=20powe= r=20supply.

&n= bsp;

As=20a=20= reminder,=20I’ve=20the=20amplifier=20will=20be=20based=20on=20a=20= Class=20D=20design.

 

“Power=20= amplifier=20circuits=20(output=20stages)=20are=20classified=20as=20A,=20B,=20AB= =20and=20C=20for=20analog=20designs—and=20class=20D=20and=20E=20for=20switching=20design= s.=20The=20power=20amplifier=20classes=20are=20based=20on=20the=20proporti= on=20of=20each=20input=20cycle=20(conduction=20angle)=20during=20which=20an=20a= mplifying=20device=20passes=20current.=20The=20image=20of=20the=20conduction=20= angle=20derives=20from=20amplifying=20a=20sinusoidal=20signal.=20If=20the=20dev= ice=20is=20always=20on,=20the=20conducting=20angle=20is=20360°.=20If=20it= =20is=20on=20for=20only=20half=20of=20each=20cycle,=20the=20angle=20is=20180&de= g;.=20The=20angle=20of=20flow=20is=20closely=20related=20to=20the=20amplifier= =20power=20efficiency.”

 

Source:=20https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amplifier#Power_amplifi= er_classes

 

Billy=20Zimmer

Engineer

Here=20is=20the=20exact=20quote=20from=20Calvin=20Coolidge…please= =20share=20it=20with=20those=20who=20might=20benefit…

 

“Nothing=20in=20this=20world=20ca= n=20take=20the=20place=20of=20persistence.=20Talent=20will=20not:=20nothing=20i= s=20more=20common=20than=20unsuccessful=20men=20with=20talent.=20Genius=20will= =20not;=20unrewarded=20genius=20is=20almost=20a=20proverb.=20Education=20will= =20not:=20the=20world=20is=20full=20of=20educated=20derelicts.=20Persistence=20= and=20determination=20alone=20are=20omnipotent.”

 

You=20can=20learn=20more=20about=20Calvin=20C= oolidge=20on=20Wikipedia:

 

“John=20Calvin=20Coolidge=20Jr.=20(July=204,=201872=20–=20Jan= uary=205,=201933)=20was=20the=2030th=20President=20of=20the=20United=20States=20(1923–29).=20A=20<= span=20class=3D"cs1B16EEB5">Republican= =20lawyer=20from=20Vermont,=20Coolidge=20worked=20his=20way=20up=20the=20ladder= =20of=20Massachusetts=20state=20politics= ,=20eventually=20becoming=20governo= r=20of=20that=20state.=20His=20r= esponse=20to=20the=20Boston=20Police=20Strike=20of=201919=20thrust=20him=20into= =20the=20national=20spotlight=20and=20gave=20him=20a=20reputation=20as=20a=20ma= n=20of=20decisive=20action.=20Soon=20after,=20he=20was=20elected=20as=20the=20<= /span>29th=20vice=20president=20in=201920=20and=20succeeded=20to=20the=20presidency=20upon=20the=20sudden=20death=20of=20Warren=20G.= =20Harding=20in=201923.=20Electe= d=20in=20his=20own=20right=20in=201924,=20he=20gained=20a=20reputation=20as=20a=20small-go= vernment=20conserva= tive,=20and=20also=20as=20a=20ma= n=20who=20said=20very=20little,=20although=20having=20a=20rather=20dry=20sense= =20of=20humor.”

 

Thanks

 =

Bart=20Arnaz<= /span>

 I=20told=20you=20I=20wa= s=20right…The=20longest=20river=20in=20the=20world=20is=20the=20Nile.=20=

 =

“The=20= Nile=20is=20a= =20major=20north-flowing=20river=20= in=20northeastern=20Africa,=20and=20is=20commonly=20regarded=20as=20the=20= longest=20river=20in=20the=20world,=20though=20some=20sources=20claim=20that=20the= =20Amazon=20River= =20is=20longer.=20The=20Nile,=20which=20is=206,853 km=20(4,258 miles)= =20long,=20is=20an=20"international"=20river=20as=20its=20drainage=20basin=20covers= =20eleven=20countries,=20namely,=20Tanzania,=20Uganda,=20Rwan= da,=20Burundi= ,=20the=20Democratic=20Republic=20of=20the=20Congo,=20Kenya,=20Ethiopia,=20Erit= rea,=20South=20Sudan<= /span>,=20Sudan=20and=20Egypt.= =20In=20particular,=20the=20Nile=20is=20the=20primary=20water=20source=20of=20E= gypt=20and=20Sudan.”=20

 

Source:=20Wikipedia.org
